### 책 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "세계를 건너 너에게 갈게",
    "author": "이꽃님",
    "price": 10000
}

### 책 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/books

### 책 한권 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/books/1


### 책 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "세계를 건너 너에게 갈게",
  "author": "이꽃님",
  "price": 11500
}

### 책 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/1